<%= provide(:body_id, 'index') %>
<%= provide(:result, '网站次命中率') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>网站次命中率数据报表</h1>

        <p>
          本排名表根据同一网站根据DNS解析的归属地进行统计，如对结果有异议，可申请核对。
        </p>
        <br/>

        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;...</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <div class="span12">
          <h4 class="title"><%= @url %>命中率汇总如下示：</h4>

          <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
          <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
            <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="text-align:center;">时间点</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">电信命中率</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">联通命中率</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <% @all_in_one.each do |line| %>
              <tr>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <!--<%# link_to line[0].strftime('%Y年%m月%d日'), action: 'list_time', url: @url ,day: line[0].strftime('%Y-%m-%d') %>-->
                  <%= link_to line[0].strftime('%Y年%m月%d日 %H点'), action: 'list_locale', url: @url ,day: line[0]%>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><span class="label label-info">
                  <% unless line[1].blank? %>
                    <%= number_to_percentage line[1]*100 %>
                  <% end %>
                </span></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><span class="label label-info">
                  <% unless line[2].blank? %>
                    <%= number_to_percentage line[2]*100 %>
                  <% end %>
                </span></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p></p>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          Etiam varius erat in nisl egestas id auctor lacus consectetur.
          Ut dui risus, auctor a malesuada volutpat, tempus sit amet arcu.
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">Jane Doe via Mobile</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>